Use the standard library
This is how to sum_product of numbers:
   Remember that total is 0
   Remember that prod is 1
   Remember that n is numbers's length
   Remember that i is 0
   Do this n times:
      Remember that x is item i in numbers
      Remember that total is sum of total and x
      Remember that prod is product of prod and x
      Increase i
   End do
   The answer is [total, prod]
Now you know